hysics in that small timeframe, but I tried my best to get all of the stuff worth knowing for most people, and explaining it as simply as possible, as fast as possible ;)\n\nTimestamps:\n00:00 Classical Mechanics\n02:33 Energy\n04:40 Thermodynamics\n06:01 Electromagnetism\n08:30 Nuclear Physics 1\n09:28 Relativity\n11:25 Nuclear Physics 2\n12:13 Quantum Mechanics\n\nThis video took way too many hours to make. \nIf you like it, show it to your friends. Thanks\n\nMusic by Audionautix.com\n\nInspired by Arvin Ash's Video: https://youtu.be/TTHazQeM8v8?si=6taX-lihz1hSNYk5","isCrawlable":true,"thumbnail":{"thumbnails":[{"url":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ZAqIoDhornk/hqdefault.jpg?sqp=-oaymwEiCKgBEF5IWvKriqkDFQgBFQAAAAAYASUAAMhCPQCAokN4AQ==\u0026rs=AOn4CLBUtlKzFP2Rhnc7Jm92bijVpVKrcQ","width":168,"height":94},{"url":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ZAqIoDhornk/hqdefault.jpg?sqp=-oaymwEiCMQBEG5IWvKriqkDFQgBFQAAAAAYASUAAMhCPQCAokN4AQ==\u0026rs=AOn4CLDdlkx9lZd-oJ39JfMUrzBOW71v0Q","width":196,"height":110},{"url":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ZAqIoDhornk/hqdefault.jpg?sqp=-oaymwEjCPYBEIoBSFryq4qpAxUIARUAAAAAGAElAADIQj0AgKJDeAE=\u0026rs=AOn4CLDbTvL_Oija1jUeQagkt5zHVHx5wg","width":246,"height":138},{"url":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ZAqIoDhornk/hqdefault.jpg?sqp=-oaymwEjCNACELwBSFryq4qpAxUIARUAAAAAGAElAADIQj0AgKJDeAE=\u0026rs=AOn4CLA_GIb0XF1V53-BUt3JRy15gJQRFw","width":336,"height":188},{"url":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ZAqIoDhornk/maxresdefault.jpg","width":1920,"height":1080}]},"allowRatings":true,"viewCount":"8084514","author":"Wacky Science","isPrivate":false,"isUnpluggedCorpus":false,"isLiveContent":false},"annotations":[{"playerAnnotationsExpandedRenderer":{"featuredChannel":{"startTimeMs":"0","endTimeMs":"839000","watermark":{"thumbnails":[{"url":"https://i.ytimg.com/an/8VhAX-voAUegprM4SpHQJQ/featured_channel.jpg?v=6592b7c4","width":40,"height":40}]},"trackingParams":"CBMQ8zciEwiJg579q5yRAxXERE8EHZZ0Peg=","navigationEndpoint":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBMQ8zciEwiJg579q5yRAxXERE8EHZZ0PegyAml2ygEElQkwGA